{
  "stem": "8775.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was much older than my father was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was also a very respected lawyer in, in Szolnok.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was one of the main members of this committee.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the committee was actually powerless.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And talking about the ghetto, I wanted to bring up this little tale about my mother's uncle and aunt.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My uncle was a converted Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he had papers, which he, he showed at the ghetto, where he had to report to, that he was converted.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they said, it doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You have to come into the ghetto anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then, what happened was that his wife, who was German and Roman Catholic, went and she was pleading with the commandant of the ghetto, who was German.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in German, she begged him, let my husband get out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he said, no way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The only way-- she said, we want to be together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She-- he said to her, the only way you can be together with, with him, if you yourself come into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she refused to do so.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So this is how they got separated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And of course, the sad story of it is that Oscar, who was my, my mother's aunt-- he was killed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My, my mother's uncle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was, he was killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we don't know the exact circumstances how.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was a decorated-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I want to say major.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he was a higher up than a major-- a colonel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a, he was a colonel from World War I who lived on pension.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the ghetto was very large.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the, the Jews from Szolnok were in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
